gel hev hazir bin bi vê qenatê.
 
Whoever wants to, whatever garden it is, whatever your heart
desires... we can be present together on this channel.

271
00:27:58,000 --> 00:28:01,000
Û hûn jî malbata min in, ez spasiya we jî dikim.
 
And you are also my family, I thank you as well.

272
