274
00:28:08,000 --> 00:28:12,000
Û ez ta'lîqan jî hazif nakim. Belkî me tiştek şaş aniye.
 
And I won't delete the comments either. Maybe we did
something wrong.

275
00:28:12,000 --> 00:28:16,000
Û bîr mekin qenata Hatim Li Efrîn da'm bikin û bimînin di
xêr û xweşiyê de. Gelek spas.
 
And don't forget to support the Hatim Li Efrîn channel, and
stay in goodness and happiness. Thank you very much.

276
